{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_10",
  "title": "星見編2章5話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "れ、怜……どうした？ 戻りが遅かったから\n心配でちょっと様子を見に来たんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rei… what’s the matter? You were late‚\nso I came to check if everything was okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 7.4666666666666694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nはい。大丈夫、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nYes. I’m fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（大丈夫と言うものの、怜の表情には陰りがあった）\n（知らない振りをするべきではない。そう思った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Despite Rei’s words‚ she seemed clouded.）\n（I shouldn’t pretend I don’t know what happened.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 22.166666666666707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、怜\nLizNoirの二人との会話、聞いてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry‚ Rei.\nI actually heard your conversation with the girls from LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 27.833333333333297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……やっぱり{user}さんは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I thought‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "覗きの常習犯ですね。最低です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really are a peeping tom. Unbelievable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 33.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない……\nけど怜のことが心配なのは本心で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry…\nBut I am really worried about you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.06666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "冗談です、分かってますよ\n真に受け過ぎです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was a joke. I know you are.\nDon’t take it seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.36666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 44.13333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……私は、焦ってたんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Do you really think I’m impatient?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.13333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 48.16666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "やるからには上を目指すしかない\nそのためには、ひたすら練習するしかない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m going to do this‚ I want to aim for the top.\nTo reach the top‚ I need to keep practicing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.96666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でもただ練習するだけじゃ\n越えられない壁もたくさんあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are so many barriers\nthat can’t be overcome with just practice….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.40000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "それをどう登ればいいのかって考えるけど\nそうしてる間にも、私を追い抜く人達がいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been trying to figure out how to overcome these barriers‚\nbut meanwhile‚ others are passing me by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.26666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 67.51540466944378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に考え始めたら、私\nいても立ってもいられなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I started thinking this way‚\nI felt like I have to do something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.48207133611045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、井川葵にあんなことを聞いたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why you asked Aoi Igawa for advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.61540466944378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 75.96540457407635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "簡単に教えてくれるとは思ってませんでした\nでも、ヒントぐらい掴めたらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t expect her to give me all the answers‚\nbut I thought I could at least get some sort of hint.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.86540457407635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 83.43207124074301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、何もないって……\nそんなこと、あり得るんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And yet‚ she said there is no secret….\nDo you think that’s even possible?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.69873790740967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 88.232071240743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "目標も何もなく、ただ普段通り努力を重ねただけで\nあんな凄いダンス……踊れるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be able to dance so incredibly without setting any goals…\njust by practicing‚ as usual‚ each day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.39873790740968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "あれに勝てなきゃ……越えなきゃ、私はアイドルとして\n結果を出せない……親にだって認めてもらえない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I can’t beat them… if I can’t surpass them‚\nI can’t succeed as an idol… my parents will never accept me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.16666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 106.96946953098953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もっともっと先へ進まないと……\nなのに、どうしたらいいのか分からない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I need to keep moving forward…\nBut I don’t know how to do it….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.10280286432288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 114.90280286432288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに怜は、少し焦っているかもしれないな\n高い目標と向上心があって、そこを目指そうと必死だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that you might be a little impatient.\nYou’ve got high goals and aspirations‚ and you’re desperate to reach them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.33613619765624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは悪いことじゃない。けど、焦って\n先を行き過ぎているように俺には見えるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not necessarily a bad thing. But it looks to me\nlike your impatience is causing you to get ahead of yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.30280286432291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 130.3694695309896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "それの何がダメなんですか？\nちょっとでも先へ……前へ進まないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong with that?\nIsn’t hard work the attempt",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.00280286432303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "それが、努力ってことですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to get as far ahead as you can?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.10280286432305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 138.55280291200677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれない。でも怜は\n一人でLizNoirと戦うわけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be so. But‚ Rei‚\nyou’re not going to fight LizNoir on your own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.45280291200683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 144.15280291200682
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 144.15280291200685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_10-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "…………あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
